    <briefdescription>
<para>Kalman filter configuration — all matrices are caller-owned. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The caller allocates all matrices via SYN_MAT_DECL and passes pointers in this config struct. The Kalman filter modifies x and P in-place during predict/update. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
